inent!![[List of states with limited recognition|Status]]\n|-\n|1||{{flag|Puntland}}||{{Nts|4285000}}||{{flagicon|Somalia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Somalia|Somalia]]||[[Africa]]||it does not seek recognition as an independent entity\n|-\n|2||{{flag|Rojava}}||{{Nts|2000000}}||{{flagicon|Syria}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Syria|Syria]]||[[Asia]]||it does not seek recognition as an independent entity\n|-\n|3||{{flag|Jubaland}}||{{Nts|953045}}||{{flagicon|Somalia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Somalia|Somalia]]||[[Africa]]||not recognized by any other state \n|-\n|4||{{flagicon|Abkhazia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Abkhazia|Abkhazia]]<ref>{{cite news |title=\u0412 \u0410\u0431\u0445\u0430\u0437\u0438\u0438 \u0437\u0430 \u0441\u0443\u0442\u043a\u0438 \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0435\u0432 \u0437\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441\u043e\u043c \u043d\u0435 \u0432\u044b\u044f\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043d\u043e |url=https://www.ekhokavkaza.com/a/30530546.html |accessdate=4 April 2020 |work=\u042d\u0445\u043e \u041a\u0430\u0432\u043a\u0430\u0437\u0430 |date=4 April 2020 |language=ru}}</ref>||{{Nts|245246}}||{{flagicon|Georgia (country)}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Georgia (country)|Georgia]]||[[Asia]]||recognised by at least one UN member state\n|-\n|5||{{flag|Artsakh}}<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.am/eng/news/568152.html |title=No coronavirus cases in Artsakh |work=news.am |access-date=25 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325142153/https://news.am/eng/news/568152.html |archive-date=25 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>||{{Nts|150932}}||{{flagicon|Azerbaijan}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Azerbaijan|Azerbaijan]]||[[Asia]]||recognised only by other non-UN member states\n|-\n|6||{{flag|Sahrawi Arab Democratic Republic}}{{efn|Part of Western Sahara occupied by [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Morocco|Morocco]] has confirmed cases.<ref>{{cite web|url=h