ises avant 14 jours \"|work=LeMauricien.com|access-date=29 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329125853/https://www.lemauricien.com/article/coronavirus-mv-trochetia-a-agalega-des-agaleens-aucun-debarquement-de-marchandises-avant-14-jours/|archive-date=29 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>||{{Nts|289}}||[[Districts of Mauritius|dependency]]||{{flagicon|Mauritius}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Mauritius|Mauritius]]||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|15||{{flagicon|Mauritius}} [[St. Brandon]]||{{Nts|63}}||[[Districts of Mauritius|dependency]]||{{flagicon|Mauritius}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Mauritius|Mauritius]]||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|16||{{flagicon|India}} [[North Sentinel Island]]{{efn|No clear estimate as the people who live there live in complete isolation. |name=|group=}}||39||[[de facto]] autonomous region of [[India]] in [[Andaman and Nicobar Islands]]||{{flagicon|India}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in India|India]]||[[Asia]]\n|}\n\n=== States with no recognition or limited recognition ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!#!!Country!!Population!!''De jure''!!Continent!![[List of states with limited recognition|Status]]\n|-\n|1||{{flag|Puntland}}||{{Nts|4285000}}||{{flagicon|Somalia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Somalia|Somalia]]||[[Africa]]||it does not seek recognition as an independent entity\n|-\n|2||{{flag|Rojava}}||{{Nts|2000000}}||{{flagicon|Syria}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Syria|Syria]]||[[Asia]]||it does not seek recognition as an independent entity\n|-\n|3||{{flag|Jubaland}}||{{Nts|953045}}||{{flagicon|Somalia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Somalia|Somalia]]||[[Africa]]||not recognized by any other state \n|-\n|4||{{flagicon|Abkhazia}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Abkhazia|Abkhazia]]<ref>{{cite news |title=\u0412 \u0410\u0431\u0445\u0430\u0437\u0438\u0438 \u0437\u0430 \u0441\u0443\u0442\u043a\u0438 \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0430\u0435\u0432 \u0437\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\