\u201320 Liga IV Neam\u021b]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Olt]]\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Prahova]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Suceava]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Teleorman]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Timi\u0219]]\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Vaslui]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV V\u00e2lcea]]\n{{Col-end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.frf-ajf.ro/bacau Official website ]\n\n{{Liga IV}}\n{{2019\u201320 in Romanian football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2019-20 Liga IV Bacau}}\n[[Category:Liga IV seasons]]\n[[Category:Sport in Bac\u0103u County]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n | country            = {{ROU}}\n | competition        = [[Liga IV Bac\u0103u]]\n | season             = 2019\u201320\n | teams              = 24\n | promoted           = \n | relegated          = \n | league topscorer   = \n | biggest home win   = \n | biggest away win   = \n | highest scoring    = \n | matches            = \n | total goals        = \n | longest wins       = \n | longest unbeaten   = \n | longest losses     = \n | highest attendance = \n | lowest attendance  = \n | average attendance = \n | prevseason = [[2018\u201319 Liga IV Bac\u0103u|2018\u201319]]\n | nextseason = [[2020\u201321 Liga IV Bac\u0103u|2020\u201321]]\n}}\nThe '''2019\u201320 Liga IV Bac\u0103u''' is the 52nd season of [[Liga IV Bac\u0103u]], the fourth tier of the [[Romanian football league system]]. The season is scheduled began on 24 August 2019<ref>{{cite web|url=https://unupetrotus.ro/echipe-noi-in-liga-a-4-a-care-debuteaza-weekend-ul-acesta-viitorul-curita-incepe-campionatul-in-deplasare/|date=August 20, 2019|title=ECHIPE NOI \u00ceN LIGA A 4-A, CARE DEBUTEAZ\u0102 WEEKEND-UL ACESTA. VIITORUL CURI\u021aA \u00ceNCEPE CAMPIONATUL \u00ceN DEPLASARE|website=unupetrotus.ro}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.desteptarea.ro/liga-a-iv-a-tot-cu-play-off-si-play-out/|date=August 7, 2019|title=Liga a IV-a, tot cu play-off \u0219i play-out|website=desteptarea.ro}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref> and will end in June 2020.\n\n== Team changes ==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===To Liga IV Bac\u0103u===\n'''Relegated from [[2018\u201319 Liga III|Liga III]]'''\n* \u2014\n{{col-2}}\n\n===From Liga IV Bac\u0103u===\n'''Promoted to [[2019\u201320 Liga III|Liga III]]'''\n* [[CSM Bac\u0103u]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Competition format==\nThe league consisted of 24 teams divided into 2 series of 12 teams and will play a regular season, followed by a play-off and play-out. The regular season is a double [[round-robin tournament]]. At the end of regular season, the first 3 ranked teams in each series will qualify for championship play-off and the winner will participate for promotion play-off to [[Liga III]]. Teams ranked 4 to 10 from each series will participate in the play-out and the last four will relegated. Teams ranked 11-12 at the end the regular season in each series will relegated to Liga V.\n\nIn the play-off will participate only teams that have legal personality and hold C.I.S.(Certificate of sports identity) issued by the Ministry of Youth and Sport and teams with at least one group of children and juniors (U19, U17, U15, U13, U11).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.frf-ajf.ro/bacau/stiri/comunicate-ajf-1/regulament-liga-a-iv-a-sezon-2019-2020-17513.html|date=September 2, 2019|title=Regulament Liga a IV-a sezon 2019-2020|website=frf-ajf.ro/bacau}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref>\n\n==League tables==\n===Bac\u0103u Series===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|source=[https://www.frf-ajf.ro/bacau/competitii-fotbal/liga-a-iv-a-seria-bacau-8386/clasament AJF Bac\u0103u] {{in lang|ro}}\n\n<!--Update team positions here-->\n|team1=FCM|team2=DIN|team3=G\u00c2R|team4=FIL|team5=NEG|team6=VNB|team7=SIR|team8=ZOR|team9=RAP|team10=FLA|team11=CLE|team12=GAU\n\n<!--Update team qualifications here (defined below)-->\n|result1=PLOF |result2=PLOF |result3=PLOF |result4=PLOT |result5=PLOT |result6=PLOT |result7=PLOT |result8=PLOT |result9=PLOT |r