Liga II]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga III]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV]]\n{{col-begin|width=75%}}\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Alba]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Arad]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Arge\u0219]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Bihor]]\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Boto\u0219ani]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Bra\u0219ov]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Constan\u021ba]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV D\u00e2mbovi\u021ba]]\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Dolj]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Gala\u021bi]] \n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Neam\u021b]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Olt]]\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Prahova]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Suceava]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Teleorman]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Timi\u0219]]\n{{Col-5}}\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV Vaslui]]\n* [[2019\u201320 Liga IV V\u00e2lcea]]\n{{Col-end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.frf-ajf.ro/bacau Official website ]\n\n{{Liga IV}}\n{{2019\u201320 in Romanian football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2019-20 Liga IV Bacau}}\n[[Category:Liga IV seasons]]\n[[Category:Sport in Bac\u0103u County]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toCSM Bac\u0103u(link changed toCSM Bac\u0103u (football)) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E2%80%9320_Liga_IV_Bac%C4%83u"}
{"title_page": "2019\u201320 Liga IV Boto\u0219ani", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n | country                    = {{ROU}}\n | competition                = [[Liga IV Boto\u0219ani]]\n | season                     = 2019\u201320\n | teams                      = 14\n | promoted                   = \n | relegated                  = \n | league topscorer           = \n | biggest home win           =\n | biggest away win           =\n | highest scoring            =\n | matches                    = \n | total goals                =\n | longest wins               = \n | longest unbeaten           =\n | longest losses             =\n | highest attendance         = \n | lowest attendance          =\n | average attendance         =\n | prevseason                 = [[2018\u201319 Liga IV Boto\u0219ani|2018\u201319]]\n | nextseason                 = [[2020\u201321 Liga IV Boto\u0219ani|2020\u201321]]\n}}\n\nThe '''2019\u201320 Liga IV Boto\u0219ani''' ('''Liga IV Givova''' for sponsorship reasons) is the 52nd season of the [[Liga IV Boto\u0219ani]], the fourth tier of the [[Romanian football league system]]. The season began on 18 August 2019<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sportbt.ro/%ef%bb%bfduminica-incepe-noul-sezon-de-liga-4-derby-in-prima-etapa/|date=August 12, 2019|title=Duminic\u0103 \u00eencepe noul sezon de Liga 4. Derby \u00een prima etap\u0103|website=sportbt.ro}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref> and will end in June 2020.\n\n== Team changes ==\n14 teams compete in this season: the top 12 teams from the previous season and two promoted teams from the Liga V Boto\u0219ani.\n\nViitorul Albe\u0219ti, champions of previous season, lost the promotion playoff against [[CSM Bac\u0103u (football)|CSM Bac\u0103u]] from [[Bac\u0103u County]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.desteptarea.ro/csm-bacau-a-promovat-in-liga-a-iii-a/|date=June 24, 2019|title=CSM Bac\u0103u a promovat \u00een Liga a III-a|website=desteptarea.ro}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://btonline.ro/2019/06/16/baraj-liga-3-viitorul-albesti-spune-adio-promovarii-dupa-meciul-tur/|date=June 16, 2019|title=BARAJ Liga 3. Viitorul Albe\u0219ti spune ADIO promov\u0103rii dup\u0103 meciul tur|website=btonline.ro}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref> and it will stay in Liga IV Boto\u0219ani.\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n===To Liga IV Boto\u0219ani===\n'''Promoted from [[2018\u201319 Liga V Boto\u0219ani|Liga V Boto\u0219ani]]'''\n* [[AS Independentul Darabani|Independentul Darabani]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.darabaneni.ro/social/ntul-darabani-obtinut-un-punct-la-dumbravita-promovat/|date=May 5, 2019|title=INDEPENDENTUL DARABANI a ob\u021binut un punct la Dumbr\u0103vi\u021ba \u0219i a promovat \u00een Liga a IV-a|website=darabaneni.ro}}{{in lang|ro}}</ref>\n* [[CS Dante Boto\u0219ani|Dante Boto\u0219ani]]\n\n{{col-2}}\n\n===From Liga IV Boto\u0219ani===\n\n'''Relegated to [[2019\u201320 Liga V|Liga V Boto\u0219ani]]'''\n* [[CS Europa Hili\u0219eu|Europa Hili\u0219eu]]\n\n{{col-end}}\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|template_name=:2019\u201320 Liga IV Boto\u0219ani#League table\n|source=[https://www.frf-ajf.ro/botosani/competitii-fotbal/liga-a-iv-a-givova-8142/clasament AJF Boto\u0219ani]\n\n<!--Update team positions here-->\n|team1=DAN|team2=ALB|team3=IND|team4=TRU|team5=BUC|team6=S\u0102V|team7=TUD|team8=\u0218EN|team9=INT|team10=CUR|team11=PVC|team12=V\u0102C|team13=FL\u0102|team14=UNG\n\n<!--Update team qualifications here (defined below)-->\n|result1=Q\n|result13=R |result14=R\n\n<!--Update team results here and then (if needed) positions above. Don't forget to update the date (update parameter)-->\n|update=17 November 2019\n|win_DAN=13|draw_DAN= 0|loss_DAN= 1|gf_DAN=50|ga_DAN= 9<!-- Dante Boto\u0219ani -->\n|win_ALB=11|draw_ALB= 0|loss_ALB= 3|gf_ALB=42|ga_ALB=18<!-- Viitorul Albe\u0219ti -->\n|win_IND= 9|draw_IND= 1|loss_IND= 4|gf_IND=54|ga_IND=25<!-- Independentul Darabani -->\n|win_TRU= 8|draw_TRU= 0|loss_TRU= 6|gf_TRU=27|ga_TRU=27